<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hobby-n">hobby <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɒbi/    美 /'hɑːbi/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>业余爱好；嗜好：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My hobbies are reading, listening to music and watching birds.
我的爱好是看书、听音乐和观鸟。</p><footer>2012 广东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Happy is the man who is living by his hobby.
醉心于某种嗜好的人是幸福的。</p><footer>——萧伯纳</footer></div></div>